each of those below can be in its own memory slot, but both individual input AND output args should be lined up after each other
---
struct fuse_in_header
struct fuse_init_in

struct fuse_out_header
struct fuse_init_out

---
in virtio_fs.c:
  virtio_fs_enqueue_req(): 
    - calls copy_args_to_argbuf which mallocs argbuf and copies input args
    - calls sg_init_one for fuse_in_header
    - call sg_init_fuse_args() for specific request input
    - calls sg_init_one for fuse_out_header
    - call sg_init_fuse_args() for specific request output
